flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 71A: Reliability and Recovery Business-Friendly Journey

  Build[New release prepared]
  Deploy[Release deployed safely]
  Watch[System health is continuously monitored]
  Issue{Any service issue detected?}

  Respond[On-call team investigates and responds]
  Recover[Rollback or restore path keeps business running]
  Learn[Team improves runbooks and controls after review]
  Stable[Service remains stable for users]

  Build --> Deploy --> Watch --> Issue
  Issue -- No --> Stable
  Issue -- Yes --> Respond --> Recover --> Learn --> Stable
